    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ToolTreaux tool belt is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life. It features a PVC quick release buckle and 2 inch web belt so you can easily attach it and remove it when no longer needed. Each tool belt comes with 9 different tool pouches designed to hold small, medium and large construction tools including a hammer, wrench, screwdriver, pliers, measuring tape, utility knife, pruners, trowels, levels and more. Our leather tool belts come with a belt strap that can adjust up to 46” in length that will fit most waists, making this a great option for both men and women. You can adjust the belt for custom comfort and make sure that your tools are handy and easy to access</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux 9 Pocket Leather Tool Belt Large Hammer Drill Tool Pouch</h2>\n  <p>The ToolTreaux tool belt is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life. It features a PVC quick release buckle and 2 inch web belt so you can easily attach it and remove it when no longer needed.</p>\n  <p>Each tool belt comes with 9 different tool pouches designed to hold small, medium and large construction tools including a hammer, wrench, screwdriver, pliers, measuring tape, utility knife, pruners, trowels, levels and more.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>HEAVY-DUTY CONSTRUCTION - ToolTreaux heavy-duty tool belt is made of high-quality, durable and lightweight suede leather that will ensure longevity Belt features a 2 inch web belt with PVC quick release buckle to easily attach and remove</li>\n    <li>9 TOOL POCKETS - Tool belt comes with 9 different tool pouches made to hold different construction and hobby tools like a hammer, measuring tape, pliers, wrench, screwdriver, box cutter, level, pruners, trowels and more</li>\n    <li>ONE SIZE FITS MOST - Leather tool belt comes with a belt strap that adjusts up to 46 inches in length to fit most waists. Adjust the belt for custom comfort and secure it during use to keep tools handy and easy to access</li>\n    <li>VERSATILE TOOL BELT - Multi-use tool belt is ideal for home improvement, crafting, gardening and hobby DIY projects. Make sure you have quick access to your tools whether you’re working inside or outdoors</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Color:</strong> black; Material: suede leather; Belt length: 46”; Adjustable: yes; PVC quick release buckle; Weight: 1.5lbs (24oz); Number of pockets: 9; Steel hammer holder: Customizable: no</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Tools/AS2103A-BLK_deluxe_tool_pouch_12pkt_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"The ToolTreaux tool belt is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 67105</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058482402</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Adjustable</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Our leather tool belts come with a belt strap that can adjust up to 46” in length that will fit most waists, making this a great option for both men and women. You can adjust the belt for custom comfort and make sure that your tools are handy and easy to access.</p>\n  <p>Although these belts were originally designed for home improvement and construction uses, they are also great for crafting, gardening and other hobby DIY projects. Keep your tools close and organized with this belt before your next project whether it’s indoors or outdoors!</p>\n  <p>Please note: these tool belts are not customizable.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ToolTreaux tool belt is constructed of durable yet lightweight suede leather that will ensure a long life. It features a PVC quick release buckle and 2 inch web belt so you can easily attach it and remove it when no longer needed. Each tool belt comes with 9 different tool pouches designed to hold small, medium and large construction tools including a hammer, wrench, screwdriver, pliers, measuring tape, utility knife, pruners, trowels, levels and more. Our leather tool belts come with a belt strap that can adjust up to 46” in length that will fit most waists, making this a great option for both men and women. You can adjust the belt for custom comfort and make sure that your tools are handy and easy to access.",
